name: Facebook Post Contents
body:
### Welcome to Facebook Post Contest Script Page.
Choose a user review by the Facebook contest. "Graph API" data received by direct printing. A random user is selected.

### Requirements
The only thing you need one Facebook Application ID {APP_ID} number. It does not require any special data.

### Authors and Contributors
You can click to @badursun send message to author.

### Support or Contact
Having trouble with Pages? Check out our [documentation]
